                        <note rend="inline" type="source">611.1531/65: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Lay</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-03-13T19:00:00-05:00">March 13, 1935—7
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>12. Your 14, March 12, 2 p.m. The Department sees no reason for making
                            any statement.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi></signed></closer>
